{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": false, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 199873, "create_time": 1654823304, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "当然，我理解政府想让一家商店关门其实很容易，让派出所、市场管理局、消防局、卫生局派人轮流检查一遍，搜查一遍，封店是可以的", "timestamp": 1654823304}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 199874, "create_time": 1654823306, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "你讲法律我都觉得有些好笑", "timestamp": 1654823306}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 199879, "create_time": 1654823353, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "您跟我说法治我都觉得好笑", "timestamp": 1654823353}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 199880, "create_time": 1654823368, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "国家从未进入紧急状态，地方政府的权力已经扩展到说一不二的地步", "timestamp": 1654823368}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 199881, "create_time": 1654823396, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "政府违法了又如何，有谁敢去起诉政府吗", "timestamp": 1654823396}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 199883, "create_time": 1654823412, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "传染病防治法第四十二条", "timestamp": 1654823412}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 199892, "create_time": 1654823533, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re Dave: 最好不是真的，不然🤭有人蚌埠住了", "timestamp": 1654823533}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 199907, "create_time": 1654823960, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "《传染病防治法》第四十二条规定：传染病暴发、流行时，县级以上地方人民政府应当立即组织力量，按照预防、控制预案进行防治，切断传染病的传播途径，必要时，报经上一级人民政府决定，可以采取下列紧急措施并予以公告：\n(一)限制或者停止集市、影剧院演出或者其他人群聚集的活动；\n(二)停工、停业、停课；\n(三)封闭或者封存被传染病病原体污染的公共饮用水源、食品以及相关物品；\n(四)控制或者扑杀染疫野生动物、家畜家禽；\n(五)封闭可能造成传染病扩散的场所。", "timestamp": 1654823960}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 199909, "create_time": 1654824026, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Dave: 还有程序问题呢，这个权力属于“县级以上地方人民政府”的“上一级人民政府”，在北京就是“北京市人民政府”。“北京市某某区文体局”我理解权限是不足的", "timestamp": 1654824026}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 199910, "create_time": 1654824030, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "谢谢Dave.", "timestamp": 1654824030}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 199912, "create_time": 1654824067, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 只能理解为文体局请示了北京政府", "timestamp": 1654824067}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 199918, "create_time": 1654824168, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Eve: 蚌埠住的人，你指的是相信中国是法治国家、相信习近平说过“依法防疫”的人吗🤭", "timestamp": 1654824168}], "create_time": 1654823194, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1654824168, "likenum": 6, "n_attentions": 6, "n_comments": 12, "pid": 61981, "poll": null, "reply": 12, "text": "我在想，某个文体局或者卫生局一纸行政令，以防控疫情为由，让一大批店家取消堂食或者直接关闭，是否在法律上合乎程序呢？店家营业的权利，是有国家法律保护的，具体哪条法律赋予了政府关闭一家商店的权利？\n", "timestamp": 1654823194}}